Class AbstractTeam

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.ccs.cs5004.problem2.AbstractTeam

    AmericanFootballTeam, BaseballTeam, SoccerTeam

    public abstract class AbstractTeam
extends Object
    Represents detailed information of a team. including name, league, games played and remaining, points and last game played.
